column5: Anyone up for a chat?  I took the day off....
Souldn't you be out fishing then?

Love to chat, but gotta work!  Where are the walleye now?!!  Relax and enjoy the day!
The walleye are in the water....cause that's where we put them after we catch em.
Ben and I were able to get it out of him.All he said was,take my wife,PLEASE.
